<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/473705-i-really-want-to-read-this-book-but-the">I really want to read this book but the cover makes me feel ill!! Anyone else feel the same way? It&#39;s the holes! :(</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_473705'><a id="like_count_community_question_473705" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/473705?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">77 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F18798983-the-wrath-and-the-dawn">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/473705-i-really-want-to-read-this-book-but-the">6 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/473705-i-really-want-to-read-this-book-but-the">See all 32 answers</a>
</li>
